 Toyin Abraham, a Nollywood actress, has expressed her gratitude for her spouse Kolawole Ajeyemi‘s love and respect for her yesterday. The father of two remarked in a recent interview that having a decent wife leads to advancement for a guy, and that he loves his wife the most, followed by his children and mother. READ MORE: I love my wife more than my mother — Actor Kolawole Ajeyemi Toyin Abraham reciprocated by sharing a loving photo of herself and her spouse with the comment, “After God na you.” During an interview session shared on his YouTube Channel he said:  “My wife is the one thing I love the most, though I also love my kids and my mother”.